Let's find out.

00:00:34.920 --> 00:00:39.930
The original iPad really shook up the tablet
market in 2010 and it was another example

00:00:39.930 --> 00:00:45.560
of Apple innovating, but since then there
hasn't been many groundbreaking changes until

00:00:45.560 --> 00:00:47.170
now.

00:00:47.170 --> 00:00:54.030
The LG G Pad 8.3 is LG's shot at finding a
midway between the iPad Air and iPad Mini,

00:00:54.030 --> 00:00:58.239
it's larger than the Mini but still smaller
than the Air.

00:00:58.239 --> 00:01:04.030
Google has taken a real chance with LG as
the 8.3 is the first Google Play Edition tvablet

