00:01:55.640 --> 00:02:25.710
We're going to start off with the build quality,
which may be the best things about each of

00:02:25.710 --> 00:02:26.710
these tablets.

00:02:26.710 --> 00:02:33.120
This newer generation got a new design upgrade
from the previous 4th gen iPad.

00:02:33.120 --> 00:02:37.870
This makes the iPad Air quite literally a
blown up iPad Mini Retina, which in my opinion

00:02:37.870 --> 00:02:39.590
is a good thing.

00:02:39.590 --> 00:02:45.710
Both the Air and G Pad have a solid aluminum
construction that not only looks great, but

00:02:45.710 --> 00:02:47.390
also feels great.

00:02:47.390 --> 00:02:52.050
The G Pad has more of a brushed aluminum look
while the Air has a solid color, either space

00:02:52.050 --> 00:02:54.569
grey or silver.

00:02:54.569 --> 00:02:58.021
The only thing I've been disappointed with
is the speakers on both the iPad and also

00:02:58.021 --> 00:02:59.900
G Pad.

00:02:59.900 --> 00:03:04.220
The G Pad's speakers are located on the back
which makes them an ideal location to be covered

00:03:04.220 --> 00:03:05.840
up and muffled.

00:03:05.840 --> 00:03:09.830
The iPad's sound quality is less than stellar
and it would've been nice if they were a bit

00:03:09.830 --> 00:03:20.040
louder.

00:03:20.040 --> 00:03:23.860
As far as how the tablets feel in the hand,
they're very similar because of the aluminum

00:03:23.860 --> 00:03:25.220
body.

00:03:25.220 --> 00:03:29.170
The main difference however is the actual
size of each of them.

00:03:29.170 --> 00:03:35.989
Obviously the Air isn't a one handed device,
but the G Pad is somewhat usable with one

00:03:35.989 --> 00:03:37.370
hand.

00:03:37.370 --> 00:03:43.840
As far as the actual dimensions of each device
goes, the G Pad measures in at 216mms in height

00:03:43.840 --> 00:03:52.860
and 126mms in width while the Air towers over
it coming in at 240 mms tall and 170 mms wide.

00:03:52.860 --> 00:03:57.909
Ever since using smaller form factor tablets
like the Nexus 7 and G Pad I've found that

00:03:57.909 --> 00:04:03.090
