isn't mind blowing or amazing.

00:04:41.449 --> 00:04:45.710
You might have noticed in my speed test comparison
how dim the G Pad was, and that's something

00:04:45.710 --> 00:04:47.440
I've had issues with.

00:04:47.440 --> 00:04:53.039
I enjoy the larger display of the G Pad, but
the iPad Air wins 10 times out of 10 in terms

00:04:53.039 --> 00:04:54.479
